<i>♪ There is nothing</i>
<i>can console me ♪</i>

850
01:00:58.720 --> 01:01:02.360
<i>♪ But my jolly sailor bold ♪</i>

851
01:01:20.600 --> 01:01:22.640
Lord save me.

852
01:01:26.200 --> 01:01:29.160
Man, look. Look there.
[gasps]

853
01:01:29.240 --> 01:01:31.240
[grunts]
You'll scare her off!

854
01:01:31.320 --> 01:01:33.280
Aye, and good riddance!

855
01:01:37.760 --> 01:01:39.480
Can you talk?

856
01:01:41.840 --> 01:01:43.120
Yes.

857
01:01:50.640 --> 01:01:51.960
You're beautiful.

858
01:01:53.440 --> 01:01:57.000
Are you the one who sings?
[Scrum] Aye.

859
01:01:59.760 --> 01:02:02.360
Are you my jolly sailor bold?

860
01:02:02.800 --> 01:02:04.040
[chuckles]

861
01:02:04.440 --> 01:02:07.200
Aye, that I be.
Scrum, comport yourself!

862
01:02:07.320 --> 01:02:10.680
Boys! There ain't much
been given to me

863
01:02:10.760 --> 01:02:13.080
in my brief, miserable life,
there's the truth in it.

864
01:02:13.160 --> 01:02:14.680
But, by God,
I'll have it said

865
01:02:14.760 --> 01:02:18.040
that Scrum had himself a kiss
from a proper mermaid!

866
01:02:18.120 --> 01:02:20.000
[grunts]

867
